info.author: Ian Bicking
info.description:
This project aims to make `Django <http://www.djangoproject.com/>`_
applications available as encapsulated Python applications, usable by
`Python Paste <http://pythonpaste.org/>`_ (and specifically `Paste
Deploy <http://pythonpaste.org/deploy/>`_).

This has not been released yet, but you can install from the
`Subversion repository
<http://svn.pythonpaste.org/Paste/DjangoPaste/trunk>`_ using
``easy_install DjangoPaste==dev``.
info.name: DjangoPaste
info.summary: Integration of Python Paste and Django
